Nurses are the #UnseenAthletes of healthcare. 💪🩺

With everything you lift over the course of a shift, you probably can cancel that gym membership. 

Fill in the blank: “After a 12 hour shift, my arms usually feel like I’ve been lifting  _________.”

Tell us in the comments below and tag a friend for a chance to win a carefully curated gift box with products from @therabody @bombas @careandwear @wearkizik @spongellebeyondcleansing plus a spa voucher to help your body recover from the physical demands of a shift.
